  <preface>
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <para>libtinymail is a set of libraries that make building a lightweight 
	e-mail client more easy.</para>
    <para>They are designed around reducing both memory and cpu usage. They
	also try not to make to much strict dependencies or make a specific
	technology dependency replaceable.</para>
  </preface>

